FBIS4-22126 "jptot017__l94065" JPRS-TOT-94-017-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 20 April 1994 WEST EUROPE GREECE PLO Figure, Public Order Minister Discuss Terrorist Groups PLO Figure, Public Order Minister Discuss Terrorist Groups NC2004154194 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1130 GMT 20 Apr 94 NC2004154194 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] Hakam Bal'awi, the Palestine Liberation Organization's public order minister, began an official visit to our country today. This morning, Bal'awi met Public Order Minister Stilianos Papathemelis and discussed issues relating to terrorism and, particularly, the possibility of cooperation involving 17 November and ELA [Revolutionary People's Struggle] and Arab extremist organizations.
